title: RBC's Narayan: Mathematically, Tesla Not An Auto Company
description: RBC Capital Markets Global Autos Lead Equity Analyst Tom Narayan joins Bloomberg Businessweek Daily to discuss Tesla's latest earnings results, including plans to retire the Model S and Model X. Narayan says that Tesla's time as an automaker is "in the past," adding that based on valuation versus new car sales, "mathematically, [Tesla] is not a car company... it's an autonomy company." Narayan speaks with Carol Massar and Tim Stenovec. (Source: Bloomberg)
